# Routing

The problem with IP routing:

$ ssh $(head -1 router_ips)

$ internal_util/bgplist -t 8.8.8.8
CIDR			IP		HOPS	PROPERTIES	PRIORITY
8.8.8.0/20		8.8.8.0		2			2
8.8.0.0/16		12.32.76.98	5			3
8.8.8.8/32		1.3.3.7		1	LD		1 <<<<<<


PROPERTIES: L	Least hops
PROPERTIES: D	Narrowest range

$ internal_util/asnof 1.3.3.7
AS18784 mcdonalds.com USA ipv4=243968 ipv6=9223372036854775808

$ internal_util/bgplist -t 1.1.1.1 | grep 1.3.3.7
1.1.1.1/32		1.3.3.7		1	LD		1 <<<<<<

$ internal_util/bgplist --from 1.3.3.7
CIDR			IP		HOPS
0.0.0.0/0		1.3.3.7		1
0.0.0.0/32		1.3.3.7		1
0.0.0.1/32		1.3.3.7		1
